{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1707-03_19"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Réjouissances faites à Montauban]*"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mars 1707 [tome 3], p. 19-29."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le jour qui avoit esté marqué pour faire des réjoüissances à Montauban, à l’occasion de la naissance de Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne, M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " le Gendre qui en est Intendant, fit des liberalitez à tous les malades & à tous les pauvres de la ville sans exception, ainsi qu’à tous les Convents de Religieux, & procura la liberté à plusieurs prisonniers. Il monta ensuite à cheval avec un grand nombre de Gentilshommes & d’Officiers qui s’étoient assemblez à Montauban, pour prendre part à cette feste. Il traversa toute la Ville & distribua dans les places publiques, beaucoup d’argent au peuple qui ne cessa point de donner des marques de sa joye & de crier "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "vive le Roy & Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": ". Deux fontaines de vin coulerent pendant toute la journée à la porte de cet Intendant. Toute la Ville fut illuminée à l’entrée de la nuit, & l’on tira un feu d’artifice que l’on avoit dressé dans un pré sur le bord de la Riviere du Tarn, vis-à-vis du Pont."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "La Maison de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " l’Intendant, toutes celles de la Ville, du Fauxbourg, le Pont & les Isles mesme qui sont sur la Riviere, furent éclairées d’une maniere tres-singuliere, chacun ayant cherché à l’envi à donner des marques de sa joye."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Les deux costez de la Riviere étoient bordez de fusées qui tirerent pendant plus de deux heures, en se joignant en Arc-en-Ciel."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout cet artifice ayant cessé de tirer, on servit à l’Intendance un superbe souper sur quatre tables differentes, sur lesquelles il y avoit cent cinquante couverts pour toutes les personnes du beau sexe les plus qualifiées de la Ville, & qui furent servies par autant de Cavaliers, chacune en ayant un devant elle. Tout ce que la saison a de plus exquis & de plus nouveau, fut servi dans ce repas. Le bal succeda à ce souper. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[2]", "text": " le Gendre avoit fait mettre dans la plus grande salle de cet Hostel, quatre Tableaux qui estoient accompagnez des Inscriptions suivantes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Premier Tableau."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce Tableau representoit le Roy ayant la Couronne sur la teste, & à ses costez Monseigneur le Dauphin, Monseigneur le Duc de Bourgogne & Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne ; ces trois Princes avoient des Couronnes suspenduës sur leurs testes, & tenuës chacune par une main qui sortoit d’une nuë. On lisoit les vers suivans dans le mesme Tableau."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Non interrupti dat pignus amoris."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Loüis dans le Duc de Bretagne"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Reçoit un gage precieux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "De la faveur des Cieux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui toûjours l’accompagne,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Comblé de benedictions ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il voit dans sa famille auguste"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les quatre generations"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tant de fois promises au juste."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Deuxiéme Tableau."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On voyoit dans de ce Tableau Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne vêtu en Amour, tenant à chaque main une branche d’Olivier qu’il presentoit au Roy & à Monsieur le Duc de Savoye. Deux Colonnes estoient placées aux deux costez de Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne, avec ces deux vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Prælia jam cessent, vestri sim nodus amoris,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Me sine tela, volant me veniente cadant."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "TRADUCTION."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Si ma naissance a pour vous quelques charmes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Daignez-vous rendre à mes tendres souhaits,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "En ma faveur quittez les armes,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Et que je sois le nœud d’une éternelle paix."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Troisiéme Tableau."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce Tableau faisoit voir un Fleuve appuyé tranquillement sur son Urne, & voyant grossir ses eaux à mesure qu’elles s’éloignoient de leur source, Symbole de la durée, & de l’accroissement de la Maison de Bourbon, par la naissance de Monseigneur le Duc de Bretagne, avec ces mots tirez d’un Vers de Virgile."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vires que acquirit eundo."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "TRADUCTION."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Plus il s’éloigne